{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/gamedev/best-practices-of-game-jams","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Jamming gives very unique feeling that I've never had at work.\nAfter thorough planning on paper and in Confluence I tirelessly code and code and code.\nNo questions, no meetings, no watercooler breaks. Ideal life ü¶Ñ</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-evening-brainstorm-\" style=\"position:relative;\">#1 Evening brainstorm üçµ<a href=\"#1-evening-brainstorm-\" aria-label=\"1 evening brainstorm  permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>search for jams in progress when a 3-day weekend is ahead</li>\n<li>find out a theme</li>\n<li>make a cup of tea</li>\n<li>think about simple and fun mechanics</li>\n<li>then go to sleep, write code tomorrow</li>\n<li>if you don‚Äôt have ideas even after the second cup of tea, then you are not going to sleep today. Think better brain!</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-finish-it-at-any-cost\" style=\"position:relative;\">#2 Finish it at any cost<a href=\"#2-finish-it-at-any-cost\" aria-label=\"2 finish it at any cost permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>cut the scope</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"3-get-your-environment-ready\" style=\"position:relative;\">#3 Get your environment ready<a href=\"#3-get-your-environment-ready\" aria-label=\"3 get your environment ready permalink\" class=\"with-anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">\n                <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3\n                3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3\n                  9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64\n                  1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">\n                </path>\n                </svg></a></h2>\n<p>Check that you have all tools installed</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Krita</li>\n<li>GIMP</li>\n<li>Inkscape</li>\n<li>Soundly</li>\n<li>LMMS</li>\n<li>Godot 3.4.4.stable</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Installed? Then you are ready to jam!</p>","excerpt":"Jamming gives very unique feeling that I've never had at work.\nAfter thorough planning on paper and in Confluence I tirelessly code and code‚Ä¶","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-evening-brainstorm-\">#1 Evening brainstorm üçµ</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-finish-it-at-any-cost\">#2 Finish it at any cost</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#3-get-your-environment-ready\">#3 Get your environment ready</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"socialcard":"gatsby-plugin-social-card/b53f8946-bfb7-51ec-8349-82476f6abb67.jpg"},"frontmatter":{"date":"May 27, 2022","published":"June 07, 2022","lastModified":"A